Read in data

ped <- read.table("../cov19_snp/cov19.ped", header = F)
info <- read.table("../../sample_info.txt", header = T)

Modify data

#rename chromosome
map$V1 <- "genome"
#write to output

#assign group
ped$V1[1] <- "reference"
ped$V1[2:1931] <- info$state
#set V1 as factor
ped$V1 <- as.factor(ped$V1)
